Class YetiLog

java.lang.Object
  yeti.YetiLog

public class YetiLog
extends java.lang.Object

Class that manages logging in Yeti. The generated test cases are also part of the logging mechanism.

Author:
Manuel Oriol (manuel@cs.york.ac.uk)
